PKG_SHORTDESC="VDR -- pvrinput plugin"
PKG_LONGDESC="vdr-pvrinput is a plugin for VDR, the Video Disk Recorder. It enables the usage of Hauppauges PVR x50, PVR500, PVR USB2, HVR1900 or HD PVR as MPEG input devices."
